node.title: Eight injured in three-car crash in Pt Chevalier
node.content: ["Eight people have been injured including one who was taken to hospital in a crash in the Auckland suburb of Pt Chevalier.", "St John says the crash happened at around 8:20am and involved three cars.", "Seven of the injured had minor injuries while one had serious injuries and was taken to Auckland Hospital.", "Auckland Transport said Great North Rd between Moa Rd and Motions Rd is down to one lane eastbound as a result of the crash.", "Travel delays should be expected."]
